.TH RESTLESS 1 "2026-04-17" "restless" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
restless \- discover, map, inspect, and call APIs from the terminal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B restless
.I target-url
.br
.B restless
.I command
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B restless
is a terminal-native API topology discovery engine. It discovers unknown API surfaces, infers structure, and renders a topology graph directly from a target URL.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B restless https://api.github.com
Probe an API target directly, infer structure, and render an SVG topology graph.
.TP
.B restless discover https://api.github.com
Run the explicit discovery subcommand.
.TP
.B restless map
Render cached endpoint topology.
.TP
.B restless completion bash
Generate bash completion to standard output.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B discover
Discover API endpoints.
.TP
.B learn
Discover and cache endpoints for later commands.
.TP
.B map
Render cached API topology.
.TP
.B inspect
Inspect a cached route.
.TP
.B call
Call an API endpoint.
.TP
.B graph
Render graph output.
.TP
.B completion
Generate shell completion.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B *.svg
Topology graph output written in the current working directory when running direct target mode.
